            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1637066574658-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1637066574658-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the <strong>white long grain rice </strong>until the water runs clear, then add to<strong> </strong>an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>with<strong> </strong>the <strong>grated carrot</strong>,<strong> chopped ginger</strong>,<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>and<strong> </strong>225ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, cover tightly with<strong> tin foil </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 30 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>zesty</strong> <strong>carrot & ginger rice</strong></p><p>Once cooked, remove from the oven and keep covered until serving</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1637066578974-x200.jpg",
