      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice the <strong>remaining spring onions</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Roll the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
