    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into wedges</p><p>Slice the <strong>Hainanese-style chicken</strong> and serve it over the <strong>sliced tomato</strong> and <strong>cucumber discs</strong> with the <strong>zesty carrot & ginger rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>fragrant lime dressing</strong> over the chicken, then garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong> and the <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
